B.Cy=new A.dp("How should I care for my jewelry?","To help preserve the beauty and longevity of your jewelry, avoid exposing it to water, perfumes, lotions, cleaning products, and other harsh chemicals. Jewelry should be removed before swimming, bathing, exercising, or sleeping.")
B.Co=new A.dp("How should I store my jewelry?","Store your jewelry in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and moisture. When not being worn, keeping pieces in a jewelry box or soft pouch can help prevent damage and tangling.")
B.Cq=new A.dp("Will my jewelry last?","With proper care, handmade jewelry can be enjoyed for years to come. Treating your jewelry with care will help preserve its appearance and durability.")
B.Cp=new A.dp("Does my order include care instructions?","Yes. Every Luminary Lightwork order includes a jewelry care card with instructions to help you care for your pieces.")
