B.Ci=new A.kc("Jewelry Care",B.FF)
B.CB=new A.dp("How do I determine my bracelet size?","Use a flexible measuring tape to measure your wrist snugly. If you do not have a measuring tape, a piece of string can be wrapped around your wrist and measured against a ruler.")
B.Cn=new A.dp("What size should I order?","Bracelets are designed to fit comfortably while allowing natural movement. Please refer to the sizing guide provided on each product listing for specific recommendations.")
B.Cu=new A.dp("What if I need a custom size?","Custom sizing may be available for select designs. Please contact Luminary Lightwork before placing your order to discuss custom sizing availability.")
B.Gr=A.a(s([B.CB,B.Cn,B.Cu]),t.Ix)
B.Cm=new A.kc("Sizing",B.Gr)
B.Cv=new A.dp("How long will it take to receive my order?","Processing times vary depending on order volume and product availability. Current processing times will be listed at checkout.")
